        "Command-line tool"
      ],
      "sc:author": "Nick Borcherding",
      "sc:citation": {
        "@id": "https://doi.org/10.18129/B9.bioc.immReferent"
      },
      "sc:description": "Provides a consistent interface for downloading, storing, and accessing immune receptor (TCR/BCR) and HLA sequences from IMGT, IPD-IMGT/HLA, and OGRDB (AIRR-C). Supports export to popular analysis tools including MiXCR, TRUST4, Cell Ranger, and IgBLAST. This package serves as a core dependency for immunogenomics packages, ensuring reliable and high-quality sequence access with local caching for reproducibility.",
      "sc:license": "MIT",
      "sc:name": "immReferent",
